      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of solver setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts by a qualified analyst not involved in the original simulation.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup was conducted. Single analyst performed all setup and post-processing. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
