      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions required for all uncertain model inputs; Monte Carlo propagation to QoIs required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Nominal values used for all model inputs including blood viscosity, hemolysis model constants, and surface roughness. No probability distributions assigned. Monte Carlo UQ not executed. Flagged as epistemic gap."
