      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample size justification and repeatability assessment required for hemolysis experiments.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis experiments conducted with n=3 replicates without power analysis justification. Inter-sample variability reported but not propagated to validation metric. Flagged as epistemic gap."
